title: Was This Mother Followed By A Dark Entity? | True Ghost Stories
description:
Today on a chilling new episode of Real Ghost Stories Online.

What happens when a young mother-to-be finds herself being followed by a dark energy. 

What can this innocent woman do to rid herself of this force that seems to want to take over her life, and the life of her unborn child. 

We’ll dive deep into this story, and much more, today, On real ghost stories Online.

If you have a real ghost story or supernatural event to report, please write into our show or call 1-855-853-4802!
